PrecisREGULATIONS AMENDING THE IMMIGRATION REGULATIONS, 1978 which create a new class of immigrants, the "Undocumented Convention Refugee in Canada Class", that will allow for the granting of permanent residence status to refugees from Afghanistan and Somalia who are without proper identity papers.
